Claire Stansfield https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Claire_Stansfield 0 Claire Stansfield (born 27 August 1964) is an English-Canadian actress, director, fashion designer and former model. She is best known for her recurring role as "Alti" in several episodes of the TV series Xena: Warrior Princess.
